high_descs: Turn right, move towards the nightstand, and when you get there, turn to face the bed.
Pick up the book from the bed that's closest to you.
turn right and move to the white and gray table across the room.
Place the book on the table to the right of the CD.
Turn around and move back to the nightstand and face the bed.
Pick up the next closest book to you, which is next to the computer.
Turn around and carry the book back to the table across the room.
Place the book on the table to the right of the other one you previously left there.
anns.task_desc: Move two books to a table.

high_descs: Turn right, turn right at the night stand and face the bed.
Pick up the book on the bed closest to you.
Walk over to the desk on the other side of the room.
Put the book down on the desk to the right of the CD.
Move back over to the side of the bed.
Pick up the book to the left of the lap top.
Move back over to the desk.
Put the book down on the desk to the right of the first book.
anns.task_desc: To move two books to the desk.

high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the side of the bed.
Pick up the closest book off of the bed.
Turn right and walk towards the door, then hang a left and walk to the table against the wall on the right.
Put the book on the table to the right of the disc.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, then hang a right and walk towards the night stand, turn right again to face the bed.
Pick up the closest book off of the bed.
Walk over to the table that is against the wall on your right.
Put the book on the table to the right of the book that is already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two books from the bed to a table.
